oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jackie Christian and Robert Spicer dancing at Granny's Restaurant
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Jackie Christian and Robert Spicer take a turn on the dance floor at Granny's Restaurant in Dickson, TN, 1984.
Spicer, a 1990 National Heritage Fellowship honoree, trained generations of dancers in the Middle Tennessee region.
